          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " NE102 plastic scintillator 1.25 cm thick, 6.5",
                "cm in diameter. The three neutron TOF spectrometers",
                "are nearly identical. Each detector consists of a",
                "plastic scintillator mounted on a photomultiplier."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The scatterer comprised of two Canadian gold maple",
                "leaf coins of total mass 62.352 g. This unusual",
                "choice of scatterer was chosen because it was",
                "convenient and readily available while meeting our",
                "disk shaped design requirements. With such a small",
                "scatterer, (thickness 0.56 cm, diameter 3.O cm)",
                "multiple scattering corrections were neglected. Where",
                "it should be noted that for the neutron energies",
                "discussed, their mean free path in 197Au is",
                "approximately 3.5 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two experiments for the differential angular",
                "distributions at 1.0 MeV, 1.5 MeV and 2.0 MeV and the",
                "total neutron cross section measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainties were deduced from the",
                "covariances using the Donald Smith prescription.",
                "Mathematical formalism is given but no covariance",
                "matrices, uncertainties are graphically plotted."
              ]
            }
